OL,7,FPubs are facing steeper business taxes
OL,8,Fthat could cost the sector an extra
OL,9,F#150 million and threaten thousands of
OL,10,Fjobs, new analysis suggests.
OL,12,FFirms will end up paying more despite
OL,13,Fbusiness rates being lowered in the
OL,14,FBudget, industry bosses are warning.
OL,16,FThis is because they are facing a cut
OL,17,Fto existing tax relief next year,
OL,18,Fcoupled with revaluations that could
OL,19,Fpush up how much pubs can be taxed.
