OL,5,Canalysis
OL,7,FNew analysis from the British Beer and
OL,8,FPub Association (BBPA) estimates that
OL,9,Fhigher bills will cost the industry an
OL,10,Fextra #150 million ` the equivalent to
OL,11,F12,500 jobs.
OL,13,FThe BBPA calculated that bills will
OL,14,Frise by #3,867 for the average small
OL,15,Fpub from next year, and by #11,085 for
OL,16,Fthe average medium-sized pub.
