OL,7,FEmma McClarkin, chief executive of the
OL,8,FBBPA, said pubs across the country
OL,9,F"are anxiously doing the sums and many
OL,10,Fwill now see their bills will
OL,11,Fdramatically go up, not down, despite
OL,12,Fthe impression the Budget gave".
OL,14,F"The new lower multipliers combined
OL,15,Fwith the loss of the existing relief
OL,16,Fwill not counter the huge increase in
OL,17,Frateable values," she told the Press
OL,18,FAssociation.
