OL,7,FIn the Budget, the Government
OL,8,Fconfirmed a current 40% discount for
OL,9,Fretail, hospitality and leisure
OL,10,Fbusinesses ` which is capped at
OL,11,F#110,000 per business ` will end on
OL,12,FMarch 31 next year.
OL,14,FThis will be replaced by a new system
OL,15,Ffrom the next financial year, which
OL,16,Fwill see rates multipliers for retail,
OL,17,Fhospitality and leisure firms set 5p
OL,18,Flower than the standard rate with no
OL,19,Fcap in support.
