OL,7,FRachel Reeves said it would be the
OL,8,F"lowest rates since 1991" and would be
OL,9,Fpaid for through higher rates on
OL,10,Fproperties worth more than #500,000 `
OL,11,Fincluding the warehouses used by
OL,12,F"online giants".
OL,14,FHowever, the discount is less generous
OL,15,Fthan the 20p reduction it could have
OL,16,Fbeen, industry groups say.
