OL,7,FAnd analysis since Wednesday's Budget
OL,8,Fhas indicated that the change,
OL,9,Fcombined with an increase in rateable
OL,10,Fvalues for most pubs, will result in a
OL,11,Fsharp annual increase to bills.
OL,13,FSeparate calculations by industry
OL,14,Fgroup UKHospitality found that the
OL,15,Faverage pub's business rates, even
OL,16,Fwith the reduced multiplier, will
OL,17,Fincrease by 15% next year ` amounting
OL,18,Fto an extra #1,400.
