OL,7,FBy 2027-28, the average pub's rates
OL,8,Fwill be #4,500 higher than today, and
OL,9,Fby 2028-29, they will be #7,000
OL,10,Fhigher, according to its analysis.
OL,12,FKate Nicholls, chair of UKHospitality,
OL,13,Fsaid plans in the Budget were "quickly
OL,14,Funravelling".
OL,16,F"We repeatedly warned the Treasury
OL,17,Fahead of the Budget that hospitality
OL,18,Fwould be uniquely impacted by
OL,19,Fsignificant increases to rateable
OL,20,Fvalues, due to the pandemic impacting
OL,21,Fprevious valuations," she said.
